<HEADLINE> Trail Blazers Sign Gary Grant </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	PORTLAND, Ore. (AP) -- The Portland Trail Blazers signed guard  
Gary Grant to a contract for the remainder of the season. 
</P>
<P>
	The 6-foot-3 point guard appeared in 22 games for Portland last  
season and averaged 4.8 points, 3.8 assists and 16.3 minutes. He 
had been playing for a team in Greece earlier this year. 
</P>
