	The Blazers also placed guard Bonzi Wells on the injured list  
with asthma and have waived forward Nikita Morgunov. 
</P>
<P>
	Wells appeared in six games this season, totaling 19 points in  
23 minutes. 
</P>
<P>
	Morgunov, a free agent signed prior to the season, did not  
appear in a regular season game. 
</P>
